- **Password**: `admin123`

### 3. Check API Documentation

Visit `http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/schema/swagger-ui/` for interactive API docs.

### 4. Monitor System Health

Visit `http://127.0.0.1:8000/cfg/status/` for system health checks.

